 and get an overview of the situation first.  First supply the astronauts who need it most with oxygen. Save the astronauts with the highest priority who have the least oxygen left. \n\nAlso pay attention to your health and the energy level of your jet stream. Good luck on your adventures. ", "short_description": "\"highrescue\" is a virtual reality game in which you can prove your skills as an astronaut rescuer in 4 different levels. \n"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://highlewelt.com/privacy_highrescue.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "highlewelt GmbH", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://highlewelt.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2691890164460465"}, {"id": "388572352490011"}, {"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "183622331264052"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 2, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "872750657414193"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1565276393994116"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "872750657414193"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1699383817, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "872750657414193"}]}, "liveChannel": {"nodes": [{"latest_supported_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "id": "6847214758638662", "version": "2.0"}, "id": "179075118375766", "channel_name": "LIVE"}]}, "is_for_oculus_keys_only": false,